title: Projects
description: Since learning is a huge part of getting better, find what I'm contributing to in my free-time here:

projects.title: Youtube API Exploratory Data Analysis
projects.description: An exploratory data analysis through the Youtube API covering most popular 10 sustainabiliy channels. This project provides findings for everyone interested in starting a youtube channel in the sustainability niche.

projects.title: Flowmo
projects.description: A web application to follow your flowing money. Enter your budgets and see how much you have left. Created with Typescript, Nuxt 3, Vue, Pinia.

projects.title: Weather Forecast
projects.description: A web application that lets you find the current weather forecast of your chosen location. Built with React.js, Axios and Tailwind.

projects.title: Simple ToDo App
projects.description: A simple todo app to focus on the important things. Build with Vue, Nuxt 3, Pinia, Tailwind and Vitest for testing.

projects.title: Space X Website
projects.description: Rebuild of the Space X Website with React.js, Scss, Apollo and GraphQL.

projects.title: Insurance Admin Panel
projects.description: A web application created in Typscript with React.js, GraphQL and Apollo. Have an overview of your current insurances!
